\s E’ roho yangu, sikiliza vema 
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd E’ roho yangu, sikiliza vema, wimbo wa juu unatufikia! Shangwe na raha unatuletea, amezaliwa Mkombozi wetu. \bd*
\pc \bdit Ahimidiwe Mungu wa \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ! Na duniani iwe raha na amani! \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ninafurahi kwani wimbo huo tungali tunausikia huku. Na kwa upendo Mungu aita: "Mfike kwangu, nitawapa raha!" \bd*
\pc \bdit Ahimidiwe Mungu wa \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ! Na duniani iwe raha na amani! \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Katika nchi, mbali na karibu, sauti ya \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  inavuma. Watu wa dhambi wanakuja kwake, awapokea na awaokoa. \bd*
\pc \bdit Ahimidiwe Mungu wa \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ! Na duniani iwe raha na amani! \bdit*
